[0-4] Next, the man pushes the cart into the wall, followed by another person in the same clothing pushing a white cart into the wall. Behind the man, a black utility pole and tree branches extending over the wall can be seen. The man smiles at the camera, extends a finger, then turns his head to look at the brick wall and walks forward.
